Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:03.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(456,644)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I surrender
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.05,0:01:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道那个小独眼这次有什么诈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:10.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what form of trickery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is up that miniature cyclops' sleeve this time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道你想怎么整我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're trying to pull on me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我跟你说  你绝不可能得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'll tell you right now it ain't gonna work
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.39,0:01:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没想整你  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no pulling, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看到我的和平赠礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see my peace offering?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.08,0:01:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.07,0:01:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你想欺负我不识字还是嫩了点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you're gonna have to do a lot better
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than taking a stab at my illiteracy to offend me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不懂吗  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想再跟你竞争了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm through competing with you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你之前老是热火朝天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about all those fevered attempts
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想尝试偷我蟹黄堡秘方又怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at trying to steal my Krabby Patty recipe?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前那些就只是尝试而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've all been just attempts
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且次次都失败得可悲惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and every single one a miserable failure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每每想到就感觉自己动脉塞满了焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feel my arteries clogging up with anxiety
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just thinking about it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你看点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you something
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你搞什么  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crimony, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就没听说过大扫除吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ever hear of spring cleaning?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道上次这边来客人是什么时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know when the last time I had a customer was?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我完全不记得你还有过客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I can't recall you ever having a customer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there he is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我决定彻底退出餐饮业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why I've decided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to quit the restaurant business altogether
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把海之霸变成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and turn the Chum Bucket into
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(886,212)}生日快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想把你家餐厅变成垃圾堆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to turn your restaurant into a pile of junk?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些都是小玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are knickknacks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备放我新开的礼品店拿来卖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the new gift shop I'm opening up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这一定是在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, this has got to be a joke, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是认真的  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸马上就会变成可爱小店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon the Chum Bucket will be a nice little store
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门卖小摆设跟泡泡糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for bric-a-brac and bubblegum
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but be aware
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不会卸下防备心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting me guard down
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便你防  前任死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guard away, my ex-enemy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.17,0:02:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就待在这创业  不跟你竞争了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just be here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,starting my new competition-free career
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板又编造了个无脑计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton's concocted another hair-brained scheme
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来偷我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to steal me recipe--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以睁大眼睛看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so keep your eyes peeled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(618,920)}剥 开
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就听你的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, Cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这员工真听话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's an employee who follows orders
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么怪声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in blazes is that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,838)}海霸店\N盛大开业
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉我会喜欢上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling I'm gonna like
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,售卖新奇小玩意的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this new life of novelty items
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个小聪明  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clever, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那套我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two can play at this game
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我到海霸店买的酷玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look at this cool knickknack I got at the Chumporium
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面一定藏了个话筒或者摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know there's a microphone or camera in here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我真的觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I really don't think
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面没什么怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's anything weird in there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这东西放里面保管得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just put this in here for safekeeping
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快加入你的旧日好友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Join your other friend from the past
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now nobody's getting to see anything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是他诡计的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all part of his ruse--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是表面工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just cosmetic
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他自以为能造假骗到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He thinks he can fake us out
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们要给他点厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we'll show him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要比那个造假的还会造假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna out-fake the faker
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.50,0:04:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来痞老板真的不来偷秘方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like old Plankton's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,really going through with it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.02,0:04:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下再也用不着担心他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we don't have to worry about him anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.44,0:04:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  这回可把他给折磨惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, we sure whipped him this time
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子们  已经确认安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boys, the coast is clear
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板已经改过自新了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton's turned over a new leaf
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好消息  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's some good news, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  你这小白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is, you little half-wit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道还有什么好消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know what else is good news?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于可以用那部DJ机了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can finally use that deejay system
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奏乐  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上来  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right away, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's party
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.10,0:04:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to boogie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太傻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is idiotic
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不跳舞就开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dance or you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说怎么样啊  你这小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you like them apples, you little
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's get some shut-eye
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸礼品店马上要迎来重要一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got a big day ahead of us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the Chumporium Gift Shop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.20,0:05:13.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:13.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,768)}雪花球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(994,784)}毛绒玩具
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,货架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Store shelves?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新奇玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Novelty toys?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,熔岩灯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lava lamps?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的小玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Useless knickknacks?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very convincin'
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm still not buying it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要战斗吗  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want a battle, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就给你战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give you a war
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.25,0:05:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雪花玻璃球得干净了才会快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A clean snow globe is a happy snow globe
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你骗得过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may have fooled everyone else
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还骗得过你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you might have even fooled yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但就是骗不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you ain't foolin' me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我抓了个正着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you caught me red-handed
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往日时光真美好  对吧尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those were the days, huh, Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我发现生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I found there was more to life
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比偷你秘方更有意义的事多着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than just trying to steal your formula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而在这卖新奇玩意正好有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found it all right here, in novelty items
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bupkes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顽固不化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stuck in your old ways
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bupkes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这世上有这么一件事非常确定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If there's one thing that is certain in this world
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是你肯定忍不住想要我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's that you can't resist me formula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know you want it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.22,0:06:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直都是你想骗我交出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all a trick to get me to hand over me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.01,0:06:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是不信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't believe me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也是你的问题  不关我事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's your problem, not mine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the one with the problem
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是假象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all a facade
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hoax
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A con
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掩饰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A front
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sham
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诱骗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snow job
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道瞎扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baloney with a side of flimflam
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面必有阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and an order of jive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁才有问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's the one with the problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what you've done
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我的生计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my livelihood
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure it is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这秘方你可想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this isn't the formula that you don't want
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.07,0:07:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too slow
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假装不被秘方动摇  赢取大家信任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stick to your guns and eventually we'll all believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让大家卸下防备  然后趁大家不注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soften us up, then when our backs are turned
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就要动手耍诈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you make your move
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,242)}秘方
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘了样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot something
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都浪费了这么多时间追着你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've wasted so much time chasing after you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在总算有样属于我的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I have something that's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还让我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it makes me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不到真的会有这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see the day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前认识的那位无脊椎动物怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the invertebrate I used to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming, coming
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为我今天的所作所为道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,apologize for my behavior today
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前做了一堆错事  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wasn't right what I done, and
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现我伤害了某位的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I realized I hurt the feelings of, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非常关心的一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone I care about
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still there?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要补偿你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to make it up to you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来杯汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say we grab a soda?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.07,0:08:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(416,448)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,902)}汽水
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能来  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad you could make it, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么事  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's this about, Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得既然不再是死对头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought that since we're no longer archenemies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我们可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe we can
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,start over?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我可想从头来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would like that very much
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I won
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,216)}信任亭
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样不好吧  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  往后摔就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, just fall back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我  我会接住你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trust me, I'll catch you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚真是太神了  痞老板老兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was truly amazing, Plank, old buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的能百分百信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I really can trust you 100%
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.17,0:10:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的对我意义重大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,means a lot to me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了向你证明我多信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just to prove it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你收下一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to have something
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  不用礼物的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on, now, no gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是请你收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to have this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you would even think
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在情况不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But things are different now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  这样对我意义很重大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it would mean a lot to me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're serious
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.25,0:10:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  我收下你给的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, if I take this formula from you now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总会有那么几分不信任感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there will always be a hint of doubt
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, take it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活真美好  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life is good, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure is, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.87,0:11:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.85,0:11:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我邪恶又缜密的阴谋成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My diabolical, extremely convoluted plan worked
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早该去当政客的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have been a politician
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,672)}骗到你了\N老螃蟹
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不会给你秘方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd never give you the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.46,0:11:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我装得更缜密  把你给骗到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I fooled you with an even more convoluted charade
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.81,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp40\c&H00FFC1&}一朝被蜗咬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(253.316,442)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(495.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:12:00.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(407.566,442)\frz29.52}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(533.736,694)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个阳光明媚的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a sun-tastic day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.55,0:12:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snail trail
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.18,0:12:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个海绵宝宝得管好他家宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That SpongeBob needs to keep his pet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让它进我庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out of my yard
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清理它留的脏东西可烦死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sick of cleaning up after him
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能弄脏我的宠物石头收藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my pet rock collection
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都已经不止一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't the first time
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿你恶心的分泌物弄脏我家庭院了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've soiled my yard with your revolting excretions
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是给我记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But mark this down in your little notebook
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.57,0:12:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后你再也没法得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It will be the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.25,0:13:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种多刺的廉价木头连小蜗都拦得住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This cheap splintery wood will keep even Gary out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在舒坦多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I feel safe
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你家死蜗牛赶出我家地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your shell vermin off of my property
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这位烦人黄色邻居  再有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then next time, my annoyingly yellow neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家宠物又把黏液涂满我庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your wet pet oozes on my lawn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.30,0:13:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只能呼叫抓蜗牛大队了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll leave me no choice but to call snail control
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个小怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That little monster
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He bit me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  小脏孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, dirty boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你平常不这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常这样的都是你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's just like you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,养了这么一只贱蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to raise such a misbehaved mollusk
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗才不贱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's not misbehaved
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它貌似是有哪里不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there does appear to be something wrong with him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll say
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望它打过疫苗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope he's had his shots
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然打过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.80,0:14:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疫苗全都打了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of his shots?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Affirmatory
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂犬病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For rabies?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.41,0:14:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗痘还有软壳舞蹈症呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snail pox and soft shell dance?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yupie
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,囊炎呢  巨大肿包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bagitis, lumpy-bump trump
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,青春焦虑症呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,teen angst?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep, yep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了最严重的病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's not forget the worst of them all
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯狂蜗牛症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mad snail disease
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说你家宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean your pet
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没打过疯狂蜗牛症疫苗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hasn't been vaccinated for mad snail disease?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疹子好像已经开始长起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like the rash has already started
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疹子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rash?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.52,0:14:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说说看  你喉咙疼不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me, do you have any soreness of throat?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you mention it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喉咙真有点干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my throat is a little dry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个症会毁坏你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This disease will ravage your body
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你眼睛充血  失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with bloodshot eyes, loss of balance
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子凌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,messy pants
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胸腔发痒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ticklish rib cage
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚趾甲极度不整
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,severely untrimmed toenails
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后  一旦被患病的蜗牛咬到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and finally, the bite from that infected snail
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就会变成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will turn you into
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得把你家蜗牛送去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to get that snail of yours to a doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得它咬了什么重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he bites someone important
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯狂蜗牛跑走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a mad snail on the loose
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯狂蜗牛要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mad snail is coming
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦被咬到  就会变丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he bites you, you'll turn into a zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  那疯子什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jeepers, what's with all the lunatics?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它真的太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,isn't he the cutest?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来吧  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, little buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有疯狂蜗牛症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mad snail disease is real
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被疯狂蜗牛咬到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been bitten by a mad snail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得了疯狂蜗牛症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got mad snail disease
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我也得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚有只蜗牛也咬了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snail just bit me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在插播爆炸新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt this program to bring you a news blast
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,870)}请稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,854)}爆炸新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1002)}壳中恐慌
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚收到的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐慌与疾病正在迅速蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fear and disease is spreading like wildfire
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起因是一只杀手蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as a killer snail has been
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咬到了裤头村的居民们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,biting the denizens of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使其感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Infecting them with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,222)}疯狂蜗牛症
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,普通老百姓通常会这么描述病情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask any old fish on the street and they'll tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,病菌会从咬伤处进入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that germs enter through the bite radius
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Traveling upstream
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直至全身都充满了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until the entire host body is full of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,260)}疯狂蜗牛症
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在为大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We now take you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.56,0:16:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现场连线新闻快报记者帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to Action News Reporter Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,live on the scene
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch Perkins here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正在采访本次疫情的首位感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the first victim of this epidemic
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说说看  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从什么时候开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when did you first begin to suspect
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己变成丧尸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you were a zombie?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一开始有只疯狂蜗牛咬了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, after I was bitten by a mad snail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我起了疹子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I began to get a rash
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后又失去了平衡  胸腔又发痒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Followed by loss of balance, ticklish rib cage
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有其他一些症状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a few other symptoms
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只蜗牛咬了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was bitten by a snail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉我有点失去平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel off balance
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我胸腔也发痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have ticklish ribs, too
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我又没被咬到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I haven't even been bitten
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  病菌会通过空气传播了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's spreading through the air
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新独家消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you heard it here first
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就快要惨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all doomed to a horrible demise
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪某只犯病蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks to a diseased snail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.24,0:17:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只可爱又黏黏的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that sweet and slimy snail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然会造成这么大破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would cause all this destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.78,0:17:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来吃你软绵绵的黄肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here to dine on your squishy yellow flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(492,366)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's locked
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody let me in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, come in, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也带你朋友进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And bring your friends in, too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子还挺饿的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They look hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.77,0:18:19.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不准放进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:19.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't let anyone in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他们就只是想吃蟹黄堡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they just want to dine on some krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're zombies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只想吃我们的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They only want to dine on our flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  蟹黄堡钱从你工资扣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, but it's coming out of your paycheck
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又没在这上班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't work here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  是我海绵宝宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs, it's me SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要怎么知道你没变成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how do we know you haven't become
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种吃肉怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of those voracious flesh-eaters?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃肉怪物能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could a voracious flesh-eater do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我进去  省得我被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so let me in before I'm eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's SpongeBob all right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不见得真的是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that's the real SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子非常丧尸化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He looks pretty zombie-fied
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看他脸色有多黄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at how yellow he is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丧尸会往钱包放好朋友的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would a zombie have a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of his best buddy in his wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982,202)}一辈子好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps not
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我会把眼睛放你身上盯着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I've got my eye on you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你能拔了眼睛放他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you could pull out your eye and put it on him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wouldn't that make you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也变丧尸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a zombie, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变丧尸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁敢说我们都没变丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's to say we're not all zombies?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The snail
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.62,0:19:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别靠近它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't get near it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pity of it all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不敢看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't watch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都说你是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All those people think you're a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但在我心里  你只是一只蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I know you're just a snail
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.95,0:19:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how could you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝被自己养的蜗牛感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's been infected by his own pet snail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太讽刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The irony
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.61,0:20:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  得隔离那只带病蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, we must quarantine that infected snail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得它把剩下的裤头村居民全咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he bites every last Bikini Bottomite
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住那只蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get that snail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别伤害小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't hurt him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交出蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand over the snail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是为了它好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for his own good, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你们碰小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I won't let you touch Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,理智点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop the madness, man
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯狂蜗牛症现在就要结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mad snail disease ends now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seize the snail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halt
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.64,0:20:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁说到疯狂蜗牛症吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did someone say mad snail disease?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就因为这个大惊小怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what all this fuss is about?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪来的懂哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you know about it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你问得还真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny you should ask
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先自我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吉尔吉利安医生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gill Gilliam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,808)}吉尔吉利安医生\N蜗疾家及蜗家
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗疾家及蜗家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S.D.E. + S.E.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗疾家及蜗家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"S.D.E. + S.E."?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛疾病专家及蜗牛专家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snail disease expert and snail expert
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很遗憾要给大家透露这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to break this to you all
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.73,0:21:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们所谓的疯狂蜗牛症
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that "mad snail disease" you're talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it doesn't exist
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, no such thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.94,0:21:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是个上古都市传说  是谣传
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an old urban legend, a myth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说我们不是丧尸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, does that mean we're not zombies?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不是丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是群体歇斯底里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just mass hysteria
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我脚趾甲严重不整又是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about my severely untrimmed?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这只是一般的不整而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are only moderately untrimmed
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.95,0:21:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有所谓的症状都只是常见的小病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the supposed symptoms are just common ailments
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要激动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可小蜗又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about Gary then?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是它没得病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't have a disease
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会把大家都咬了  连我都咬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why'd he bite all those people including me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.35,0:21:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题就出在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The problems right here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它的脚上扎了一根小刺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got a little splinter in his foot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定就是它产生瘟热的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this was causing him distemper
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.85,0:21:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进而出现严重的发脾气症状
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making for serious grouchy snailitis
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我就知道你没病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary, I knew you weren't disease-ridden
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you still love me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good old Gary's back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是丧尸  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're not a zombie, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.72,0:22:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.40,0:22:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题解决  皆大欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well
